headline: Flat Medicare Advantage Outlook And Revenue Drop Might Change The Case For Investing In UNH
summary: In early February 2026, UnitedHealth Group reported quarterly earnings and 2026 guidance pointing to its first annual revenue decline in decades, while proposed flat Medicare Advantage rates for 2027 raised concerns about profitability in a core business segment.
